{"tid":294580,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"學支教女咁嚴, 個女竟然搭上已婚洋腸","createTime":"2017-06-23T05:40:18.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-26T03:16:08.000Z","uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"0a4438e0a953be18584409d4926a29bdffa391e9","tid":294580,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:40:18.000Z","msg":"歌神張學友與老婆羅美薇育有張瑤華（Zoe）及張瑤萱兩位寶貝女，但學友不想女兒活在鎂光燈下，故一直對她們十分保護，可謂是最神秘的「星二代」！不過年輕人愛玩社交平台，大女Zoe亦是其中一份子，現年16歲的她經常在Instagram甫靚相，日前便上載與一個名外籍靚仔的合照，還互相留言「Love」對方，惹來拍拖疑雲！可是最奇怪的是男方在Facebook自爆已婚，「新娘」卻不是Zoe！<br />\n<br />\n隔空傳情<br />\n<br />\n不時甫相的Zoe現已亭亭玉立，驟眼看跟媽咪有幾分相似，還不介意分享性感相晒身材，未知是否與曾到英國讀書、現讀哈羅國際學校而感染熱情奔放的性格。直至近日，Zoe疑似情竇初開，爆出與外籍模特兒、樣貌有幾分似「新蜘蛛仔」Tom Holland的Mathis拍拖，日前更上載攬攬合照！相中煙韌的兩人還留言隔空傳情，Mathis先留言示愛：「I love u so much！」Zoe亦冧爆回覆：「I love u more！」幾日後，Zoe繼續上載兩人的行山照，行到㷫合合的Mathis索性除衫騷肌，可見兩人關係非淺！不過記者翻查Zoe的Instagram已不見該攬攬相，連性感泳衣相亦已被刪。<br />\n<br />\n男歡女愛不是新奇事，但今次最奇怪的是記者翻查Mathis的Facebook時，個人資料一欄中驚現已婚，但「老婆」並非Zoe而是一名外籍女子，認真撲朔迷離！對於有指Zoe與Mathis拍拖，身為爸爸的學友仍未有回覆。<br />\n<br />\n自認醋父<br />\n<br />\n事實上，雖然學友一直保護女兒，但早年曾表示對女兒拍拖冇所謂，最怕自己不知情，故希望女兒有男友時可以讓他過目。他又坦言如果女兒拍拖的話自己會吃醋，曾以為自己會激動得出手打女兒男友，但後來明白人生屬於她自己，做父親的只能放手，在旁畀意見。學友又曾講過為拉近與女兒的距離，轉用智能手機開Facebook，亦曾提醒她們在網上要注意言行，免招麻煩。<br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170623/bkn-20170623000003970-0623_00862_001.html?google_editors_picks=true\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170623%2Fbkn-20170623000003970-0623_00862_001.html%3Fgoogle_editors_picks%3Dtrue&d=bPPmmc9j%2BMC%2BUdakK3fAxdtKgwQIhJBw7VlnLihElrQ%3D&h=6a947f5e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170623/bkn-20170623000003970-0623_00862_001.html?google_editors_picks=true</a><br />\n<img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170623/photo/bkn-20170623000003970-0623_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170623080616\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170623%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170623000003970-0623_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170623080616&h=96d58f11&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n歌神,也有苦惱!"},{"pid":"5af897978cac417d5e6b6c0561c68dee1b99f7f5","tid":294580,"uid":86828,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:41:12.000Z","msg":"嘩屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63f5eed501eefb0e774e20f84578c291e23c6d17","tid":294580,"uid":42820,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:42:02.000Z","msg":"對眼<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ab5ac654f206f3b2235ceeffe76428f60d55acea","tid":294580,"uid":7903,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:42:11.000Z","msg":"個女好樣衰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"adcf740f2a7ef987f8910ca8b0a991f87a558788","tid":294580,"uid":7903,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:42:36.000Z","msg":"第一眼似劣化版舒淇"},{"pid":"0b768bedd19d02151a70f8c00ecd0079525fe3ba","tid":294580,"uid":37735,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:44:01.000Z","msg":"又係鄧文迪 feel"},{"pid":"2534f89dce18c32889a91d36bc5e02a56f8f736f","tid":294580,"uid":22974,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:45:00.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"f2c8c294dc8d4cfcb24e10989264165144c36b06","tid":294580,"uid":55981,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:48:42.000Z","msg":"食屎啦你<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"463f11d7a508f59b06c65c22f2870f21d284f785","tid":294580,"uid":17558,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-23T05:58:17.000Z","msg":"個電話遮得好， 一拎開...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"56f5544560cb1d570b40dbae51badfc91cf18c74","tid":294580,"uid":40272,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"cit